{
  "stem": "6719.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I know that the cause and the reason why it's being done is very honorable, and I'm very happy and glad that it's being done.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that's not-- my priority is this, to talk to people today that all of a sudden resettlement, as they used to call us, to be resettled, today  is called ethnic cleansing.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what's this whole horse shit all about?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're doing the same thing today that we-- that they did to us down there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we're doing it a different way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not as sophisticated anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, so you don't have people that come in, they have undressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They get their hair shorn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They go into a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If not, they go into the camp and being tortured, and killed, and murdered, and who knows what.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And today, they're doing in a different way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they walk into a village and-- and-- and the guy that lives next door all his life down there knocks the whole family off.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What's the difference?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and nobody does anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "See, we, the survivors, always say one thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We always say, hey, nobody cared about us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody did anything for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Are we doing anything for the Serbs or for the Croats or for the-- for the Muslims?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We don't do anything about it either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So who the hell-- are we going to call the kettle black?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Get ?] [? annoyed. ?] That makes me angry, very angry, and I can't vent it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Who can I vent it at?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "At my wife?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At my beautiful daughter?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At my sister?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Or at you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Or at him?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I can't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I'm very angry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So that helps you speak to the kids?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
